Use Cases: 

Repititive tasks
App deployment
Monitoring
Testing
Creating reports
Setting up servers
Rotating DB passwords 
Use Python in Ansible to customize your own modules for your own use case
Read data from csv file in s3 bucket

Cloud Computing: 
boto3 or apache lib cloud gives you the power to deploy app to the cloud using python. Maintain consistency. Can be integrated with TF. 

Container/Orchestration:
Kubernetes provides python to access their API to manager pods, deployments etc. using python

Monitoring/Alerting:
Prometheus: Extract metrics from server cpu, configure alert rule to send to group. Can also use Python with Flask to create custom monitoring apps. 

Data/Visualization: 
Analyze data in the future with matplotlib (create charts to visualize) or panda. 